ent-STClothingOuterArmorSkyWalker = PNB-4UVH exoskeleton
    .desc = Turns its wearer into a true walking tank. Uses class 3 ceramic armor plates, with side belt mounts featuring protective screens that shield the flanks - which significantly increased its weight. Standardly comes with an S10 gas mask. Its only drawbacks are very weak protection against anomalies and the long-worn pneumatics of the exoskeleton, with the construction itself having outlived its time.
    .suffix = ST, T3, PvP
